     On March 12, 2004, Apollo Group, Inc. reported via press release its results of operations for its second quarter ended February 29, 2004. A copy of this press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1. This press release is being furnished, but not filed, under Item 12 of this Report on Form 8-K.
