Apollo Group, Inc. 4615 E. Elwood St. Phoenix, AZ 85040 (800) 990-APOL (480) 379-3503 fax Internet: www.apollogrp.edu www.phoenix.edu www.uopxonline.com www.ipd.org www.fp.edu www.wintu.edu
 
Kenda B. Gonzales Chief Financial Officer (800) 990-APOL Email: kenda.gonzales@apollogrp.edu
