On April 1, 2008, we issued a press release announcing that our consolidated joint venture, Apollo Global, Inc., has completed its previously announced acquisition of Universidad de Artes, Ciencias y Comunicacin, an accredited, private arts and communications university in Chile, as well as its related entities. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
