Item 7.01 Regulation FD Disclosure
On August 5, 2008, we issued a press release announcing that our consolidated subsidiary, Apollo Global, Inc., has purchased a majority stake in Universidad Latinoamericana S.C., an accredited, private university based in Mexico City, which offers secondary and post-secondary programs. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
Item 9.01 Financial Statements and Exhibits.
(d) Exhibits.
