ments during the period beginning with the first day of that month and ending no later than five (5) business days after the end of that month. Other reasonable travel, housing and food expenses incurred by Executive while traveling temporarily away from his tax home on business (other than the expenses subject to his monthly stipend) will also be eligible for reimbursement in accordance with the Company's standard business expense reimbursement policy and the foregoing documentation and reimbursement timing provisions.
