Item 8.01 Other Events.
     Apollo Group, Inc. subsidiary, University of Phoenix, has received an Expedited Final Program Review Determination Letter from the U.S. Department of Education in respect of the Department's December 2010 review of the University's financial aid programs subject to Title IV of the Higher Education Act for the 2009-2010 award year and 2010-2011 award year to date. There were no significant adverse findings in the program review. The Department concluded that the University has initiated or completed acceptable corrective actions in respect of each compliance item identified in the review and each finding has been closed. No economic or other sanctions were imposed.
     A copy of the Department's Expedited Final Program Review Determination Letter is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Form 8-K.
