     (ii) Buyer expressly acknowledges that Buyer has not relied on any warranties, promises, understandings or representations, express or implied, oral or written, of Seller or any of Seller's Related Parties or representatives, relating to the Property or any other aspect of the contemplated transaction and that Buyer is acquiring the Property in its present condition and state of repair, "" and "", with all defects and liabilities, latent or apparent.
