     (a) . Buyer may not assign or otherwise transfer any of its rights under this Agreement without the prior written consent of Seller, which consent may be given or withheld in Seller's sole discretion. Any such assignment or transfer without such consent shall be absolutely null and void and shall constitute a default by Buyer under this Agreement. No assignment shall release or otherwise relieve Buyer from any obligations hereunder.
