     On August 2, 2011, Apollo Group, Inc. issued a press release announcing its entry into the agreements described in Item 1.01 above relating to the acquisition of Carnegie Learning, Inc. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Form 8-K.
