ting bodies. For a discussion of the various factors that may cause actual plans implemented and actual results achieved to differ materially from those set forth in the forward-looking statements, please refer to the risk factors and other disclosures contained in Apollo Groups Form 10-K for fiscal year 2012 and subsequent Form 10-Q, and other filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission, all of which are available on the Companys website at
